Gg_ilu 1.0 (I Love You)
------------------------------------------
This is just a simple map I put together while taking a break from another map I was working on.
I also wanted to see how much I could get done in 2 hours.
Don't ask about the name. (just the first thing that came to me, ahaha)
This map dances around medium to small so I wouldn't have too many people playing.

There is: 
-40 spawn points
-Buyzones
-HDR
And for your own amusement I put in a shooting range at T spawn.
Have fun!
